        "uuid": "9733e293-0ee0-4d57-9da1-d95496280ac3",
        "title": "Flat And Responsive Registration Form With Html5 Validation Part 2",
        "slug": "flat-and-responsive-registration-form-with-html5-validation-part-2",
        "markdown": "\nIn the [previous article](http://uiuxblog.com/flat-and-responsive-registration-form-with-html5-validation/) we created the html markup for our registration for now we’ve gotta style it and make it responsive for all the devices.\n\n**Create a new file and name it as Style.css**\n\n<small>*make sure to place it in the same folder as the index.html</small>\n\n```\n    body { \n      max-width: 800px; \n      padding: 30px; \n      margin: 0 auto; \n      font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \n    } \n    fieldset { \n        display: block; \n        margin: 30px 0px; \n        padding: 40px 50px 45px 50px; \n        background: #f3f3f3; \n        border: 0; \n        position: relative; \n        -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; \n        -moz-box-sizing: border-box; \n        box-sizing: border-box; \n    } \n    legend { \n      font-weight: bold; \n      font-size: 20px; \n      line-height: 34px; \n      margin: 0 0 25px 0; \n    } \n    input[type=text] , input[type=password] { \n      width: 100%; \n      padding: 10px 15px; \n      margin: 0px; \n      -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; \n      -moz-box-sizing: border-box; \n      box-sizing: border-box; \n      color: #4b545f; \n      background: #fff; \n      padding: 10px 15px; \n      border: 2px solid #ddd; border-radius: 3px; \n      outline: none; \n      margin: 0 0 5px 0; \n      -webkit-transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n      -moz-transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n      -ms-transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n      -o-transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n      transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n   } \n   input[type=text]:focus { \n           border:2px solid #8FC400;\n   } \n   input[type=password]:focus { \n           border:2px solid #8FC400; \n   } \n   .select { \n           width: 100%; \n        background: #fff; \n        line-height: 1; \n        border: 2px solid #ddd; \n        padding: 14px 15px; \n        margin: 0; \n        outline: none; \n        border-radius: 0; \n        -webkit-appearance: none; \n        background: #fff url(arrow-down.png) no-repeat 97% 20px; \n        border-radius: 3px; color: #bcbcbc; \n    } \n   .button-link-submit { \n   display: block; \n           width: 100%; \n        text-align: center; \n        font-size: 18px; color: #fff; \n        background: #F58220; \n        border: 0; \n        padding: 15px 0px; \n        cursor: pointer; \n        border-radius: 3px; \n        -webkit-appearance: none; \n   } \n   .button-link-submit:hover { \n           background-color: #2A2A2A; \n        color: #fff; \n        text-decoration: none; \n        transition: 0.6s 0 ease; \n    }\n```\n\n**Once you’ve done this try to view it in your browser and it should look like this : **\n\n[![Flat And Responsive Registration Form With Html5 Validation](http://i2.wp.com/naveensingh.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/flat-responsive-registration-form-2.png)](http://i2.wp.com/naveensingh.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/flat-responsive-registration-form-2.png)\n\n**[Download the source files](http://naveensingh.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/responsive-form-files-codextuts.zip) or see it live [Here](http://naveensingh.net/source/flat-and-responsive-registration-form/)**\n\n\n",
        "html": "<p>In the <a href=\"http://uiuxblog.com/flat-and-responsive-registration-form-with-html5-validation/\">previous article</a> we created the html markup for our registration for now we’ve gotta style it and make it responsive for all the devices.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Create a new file and name it as Style.css</strong></p>\n\n<p><small>*make sure to place it in the same folder as the index.html</small></p>\n\n<pre><code>    body { \n      max-width: 800px; \n      padding: 30px; \n      margin: 0 auto; \n      font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \n    } \n    fieldset { \n        display: block; \n        margin: 30px 0px; \n        padding: 40px 50px 45px 50px; \n        background: #f3f3f3; \n        border: 0; \n        position: relative; \n        -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; \n        -moz-box-sizing: border-box; \n        box-sizing: border-box; \n    } \n    legend { \n      font-weight: bold; \n      font-size: 20px; \n      line-height: 34px; \n      margin: 0 0 25px 0; \n    } \n    input[type=text] , input[type=password] { \n      width: 100%; \n      padding: 10px 15px; \n      margin: 0px; \n      -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; \n      -moz-box-sizing: border-box; \n      box-sizing: border-box; \n      color: #4b545f; \n      background: #fff; \n      padding: 10px 15px; \n      border: 2px solid #ddd; border-radius: 3px; \n      outline: none; \n      margin: 0 0 5px 0; \n      -webkit-transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n      -moz-transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n      -ms-transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n      -o-transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n      transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out; \n   } \n   input[type=text]:focus { \n           border:2px solid #8FC400;\n   } \n   input[type=password]:focus { \n           border:2px solid #8FC400; \n   } \n   .select { \n           width: 100%; \n        background: #fff; \n        line-height: 1; \n        border: 2px solid #ddd; \n        padding: 14px 15px; \n        margin: 0; \n        outline: none; \n        border-radius: 0; \n        -webkit-appearance: none; \n        background: #fff url(arrow-down.png) no-repeat 97% 20px; \n        border-radius: 3px; color: #bcbcbc; \n    } \n   .button-link-submit { \n   display: block; \n           width: 100%; \n        text-align: center; \n        font-size: 18px; color: #fff; \n        background: #F58220; \n        border: 0; \n        padding: 15px 0px; \n        cursor: pointer; \n        border-radius: 3px; \n        -webkit-appearance: none; \n   } \n   .button-link-submit:hover { \n           background-color: #2A2A2A; \n        color: #fff; \n        text-decoration: none; \n        transition: 0.6s 0 ease; \n    }\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><em>*Once you’ve done this try to view it in your browser and it should look like this : *</em></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://i2.wp.com/naveensingh.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/flat-responsive-registration-form-2.png\"><img src=\"http://i2.wp.com/naveensingh.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/flat-responsive-registration-form-2.png\" alt=\"Flat And Responsive Registration Form With Html5 Validation\" title=\"\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://naveensingh.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/responsive-form-files-codextuts.zip\">Download the source files</a> or see it live <a href=\"http://naveensingh.net/source/flat-and-responsive-registration-form/\">Here</a></strong></p>",
